			"index": 1,
			"condition": "",
			"prompt": "<anim cat='happy' filter='eye-only' nonBlocking='true' />I am a helper, someone to talk to, even <anim name='Affection_01' nonBlocking='true'/> a shoulder to cry on. <break size='0.3'/>But don't cry on me too much, <style set='sheepish'>water damages me.</style>",
